Angvik is a platform action game set in a joyful but unforgiving land. The
castle has been taken over by a barbarian and no one else has the courage to
confront him, so take up your father's gear and set off on a wondrous journey!

and you'll encounter all sorts of creatures to fight as well. But watch your
step! You have only one life, so if you die, you stay dead.
